nc-weapon-examine-unrepairable = [color=gray]Cannot be repaired.[/color]

## Popup messages during shooting
nc-weapon-jam = {CAPITALIZE(THE($weapon))} jammed! The cartridge is stuck in the chamber.
nc-weapon-broken = {CAPITALIZE(THE($weapon))} is broken and cannot fire.
nc-weapon-jammed = {CAPITALIZE(THE($weapon))} is jammed! Extract the cartridge.
nc-weapon-overheat = {CAPITALIZE(THE($weapon))} is red-hot and burns your hands!
nc-weapon-explode = {CAPITALIZE(THE($weapon))} explodes in your hands! Plastic and metal shrapnel flies everywhere!
nc-weapon-break-permanent = {CAPITALIZE(THE($weapon))} crumbles to dust. Repair is impossible.

## Unjamming
nc-weapon-unjammed = You extracted the stuck cartridge from {THE($weapon)}.
nc-weapon-unjamming = Extracting jammed cartridge...
nc-weapon-verb-unjam = Unjam
nc-weapon-unjam-rostovic = A good smack on the bolt — and the Rostović is back in action!
nc-weapon-unjam-rostovic-fail = The hit didn't help. Try again.
